===============
System overview
===============

The system can be designed as a language workbench [1]. This means that the
system is organised around an abstract representation (of the network), and
that this representation can be interfaced with through many different means. 

- Network specification
	- HaskellAPI
	- LowLevelAPI
	- MatlabAPI
	- PythonAPI

- Simulation backend
	- CudaBackend
	- MultiCoreCPU
	- FpgaBackend
	- ClientBackend

- ClusterComputation

- Visualisation
	- NetworkConstruction
	- NetworkSimulation
